<L>__{exterior castle estate night}
<A>__{castle's estate is like a deserted city. balconies, underlit domes, lush landscaping, abstract statues, waterfalls... tiny cameras everywhere... and not a soul in sight. kable drops over a wall and onto grass. wind in the leaves, cricket music otherwise dead silence. he keeps to the trees, making his way toward the central}
<B>__{mansion.}
<A>__{then: the sound of dogs... they come in a pack, loping across the lawn grey, more like wolves... kable readies his gun to take them out but the dogs run right past him. they round a corner and disappear. weird. kable looks up, spots a camera... and another, and another... stands to reason he's been marked already. he walks out into the open.}
